Maps an `Option<&mut T>` to an `Option<T>` by copying the contents of the
option.

# Examples

```
let mut x = 12;
let opt_x = Some(&mut x);
assert_eq!(opt_x, Some(&mut 12));
let copied = opt_x.copied();
assert_eq!(copied, Some(12));
```
